lead_paragraph: LEAD: A Federal district judge has dismissed a lawsuit brought by a high school student who refused to dissect a frog in biology class.He acted after the school agreed to let her view photographs of a dissected frog that died of natural causes to identify its body parts.

headline.main: Student Who Sued School Isn't Required to Cut Frog
